{"tid":1257604,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"EVA新劇場版 將在7/6號公開最新影片","createTime":"2019-06-25T15:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:36:59.000Z","uid":181997,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb6919bc36af65517c4b3ac717c177d5f6ffe8d","tid":1257604,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"7月6日に最新映像公開。<br />\n『シン・エヴァンゲリオン劇場版 AVANT 1（冒頭10分40秒00コマ） 0706版』をパリ・JAPAN EXPOステージから、日本各地、ロサンゼルス、上海へ世界同時上映。<br />\nまた、7月1日に公式アプリ「EVA-EXTRA」リリース。<br />\n『シン・エヴァンゲリオン劇場版』0706作戦、始動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EVA新劇場版 將在7/6號公開最新影片<br />\n7/1會有官方app EVA-EXTRA上架</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201906/3e2eb48d9f9d6e7704c366609a1fa29a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201906%2F3e2eb48d9f9d6e7704c366609a1fa29a.JPG&h=6e674d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201906/c921c499b335e170b09227248e54acab.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201906%2Fc921c499b335e170b09227248e54acab.JPG&h=c2c9f8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">資料來源：EVA Twitter:<a href=\"https://twitter.com/evangelion_co/status/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fevangelion_co%2Fstatus%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=2c9fbcf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/evangelion_co/status/</a></span>"},{"pid":"d85489b6b9b1c08ece2e4ee3332c5677fd229f9f","tid":1257604,"uid":192334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"有生之年⋯⋯"},{"pid":"27e1bd2551da582e3e77aa137178f0409bc0ef90","tid":1257604,"uid":23023,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"套劇場版等撚左成6年<br />\n仲要同你講下年先上<br />\n好心你就唔好搞套哥斯拉先到Eva 啦<br />\n庵野秀明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.